<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The method Zend_Form-&gt;setErrors(array) and Zend_Form-&gt;getErrors() are not compatibles, for example, if I use the setErrors() method and as a parameter I send the return value of the method getErrors of the same form, the errors will not be setted properly</p>

    </div>
</div>

